  U INFORMATION U 

  Typing of the dead: Overkill fuses the horror and comedy of the
  legendary House of the Dead series with unique typing mechanics
  in order to deliver a truly original gaming experience
  This gruesome shooter puts you in the middle of a mutant outbreak
  in Bayou county. Blast pieces out of the zombie horde across nine
  stages, one keystroke at a time, in order to save you and a friends
  life as you work to uncover the mystery behind the outbreak.
